{"tid":1028960,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"南非男持久秘方「GG泡伏特加」　妻試過後大讚","createTime":"2019-02-20T01:22:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-22T09:11:57.000Z","uid":32511,"like":363,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":87,"replies":[{"pid":"0337a55863ca7ca9193be1aacc2ceadcf6a69916","tid":1028960,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T01:22:52.000Z","msg":"南非36歲男子姆查利(Sboniso Mtshali)，說自己有持有的獨門秘方，就是把GG泡在伏特加裡面，然後「在床上可撐兩小時」。<br />\n<br />\n據《dailysun》報導，住在索維托(Soweto)的姆查利說，「有些人會買伏特加來喝，但我是用來提高性能力。」他會把伏特加倒在杯子裡，然後掏出GG泡在裡面，說泡了伏特加以後，他可以在床上撐兩個小時，姆查利也指出，雖然不知道長期這樣做會有怎樣的後果，但是近期這樣用以後，效果讓他相當滿意。<br />\n<br />\n姆查利說，他一年前被妻子嫌太快，自從用了這招以後妻子就不再抱怨了，姆查利的妻子約斯提娜(Jostina)說「他在床上的確是個巨人！謝謝伏特加」。"},{"pid":"328c3d2976c83c771737b2c7cc28a1f2b733f548","tid":1028960,"uid":55511,"like":192,"dislike":0,"score":192,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T01:26:08.000Z","msg":"攞黎灌腸"},{"pid":"86cfa32de73425f10d2d06ca6f0772df467ce510","tid":1028960,"uid":20867,"like":25,"dislike":73,"score":-48,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T01:38:15.000Z","msg":"抽插得太快會著火<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：青頭"},{"pid":"7359dba221a3673a3258433c5d8f720d9c66e072","tid":1028960,"uid":191926,"like":426,"dislike":6,"score":420,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T01:42:52.000Z","msg":"連登仔都係唔好試<br />\n本身快槍手變2小時<br />\n<br />\n連登仔本身就2小時"},{"pid":"602f08eed24ed3c054ce99a556a3088676bddcad","tid":1028960,"uid":217275,"like":194,"dislike":1,"score":193,"quote":{"pid":"86cfa32de73425f10d2d06ca6f0772df467ce510","tid":1028960,"uid":20867,"like":25,"dislike":73,"score":-48,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T01:38:15.000Z","msg":"抽插得太快會著火<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：青頭"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T01:43:13.000Z","msg":"條女：太那西<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cad00189b4a8a1e4de395096aef888a89b88d3f","tid":1028960,"uid":66324,"like":92,"dislike":4,"score":88,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02